    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="https://philadelphia.craigslist.org/apa/d/philadelphia-rent-with-the-right-to/7514590137.html"></div>
        </div>
Rent with the right to purchase program<br>
<br>
I’m a PA real estate agent experienced in doing rent with the right to purchase deals for people who are looking to lock in their rent and home price, and move into the house they want to live in now. Avoid future out of control rent increases!<br>
<br>
The best way to buy a home is to buy it outright, which is also something I can assist with so please get in touch! However this rent with the right to purchase program works great for people who might not be able or willing to make the commitment to buy a house right this moment.<br>
<br>
I work with a company called Home Partners that will purchase a home of your choosing. No mortgage approval is needed until you want to buy it. You don’t pick from a small list, but from all houses that are for sale on the market so long as it fits the program guidelines (which honestly does limit options in our Philly market because homes must be built no earlier than 1978, no fixer uppers, only purchase in certain areas, etc. But that’s why I’m here to help and show you which homes work for this awesome program!) Some current examples that could work are in the photos.<br>
<br>
Once Home Partners buys the house you choose, they rent it to you at a pre-set price. You can choose to rent it for up to 5 years and you can buy it at anytime during those 5 years. Each year the rent and purchase price will increase but it is set in advance so you’re never surprised. If the housing market improves and you want to buy a different house, you can walk away with no obligation beyond your rental lease. If house prices go up, the price on your home is already locked in and you have the right to buy it without any competing buyers or bidding wars.<br>
<br>
This is a rent with the right to purchase program, NOT a rent to own. So the rent you pay does not get credited to your home purchase. But in this market, what a great opportunity to lock in your pricing and avoid the headache of having to move again. Plus you can bring your pets! Yes, even large dogs. Some restrictions apply.<br>
<br>
Basics you’ll need to apply and qualify:<br>
-620 or better FICO score for all applicants <br>
-Application fee paid directly to Home Partners of $75 per household (not refundable). I will first have you do a free pre-qualification.<br>
-Documented income. Self employed welcome to apply with last years tax return and 2 months bank statements.<br>
-Income minimum 3x the monthly rent. Keep in mind that most homes that qualify for this program have rents over $2000 per month and are single family homes or row homes (no condos)<br>
-Security deposit equal to 2 months rent<br>
<br>
Get in touch to learn how you can move into your dream home now and buy it later- never move again if you don’t want to!<br>
    </section>

